rows.label: tlk43300241_01_msg0001
rows.name: Fons Maim is a capital of the arts.

rows.label: tlk43300241_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Even a no-name landscape artist
like me, working day in and day out
with no sales, can find some respect.

rows.label: tlk43300241_01_msg0003
rows.name:
My worries now are of a different kind...
You see, the distribution center has
sprung up in this square...

rows.label: tlk43300241_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It wasn't there when I'd started
painting the scene...

rows.label: tlk43300241_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It won't be long before war with
Superbia breaks out... I can feel it.
